snippet.textDisplay: What a song...what a rendition...exceptional pieces on Flute, Harmonium, dholak...voices of Sajjad Ali & Fariha Parvez gel so well... Have always been a big fan of Coke Studio Pakistan...& u guys keep coming up with gems after gems... Please showcase all this talent all over the world...we Indians would love to welcome all Pakistani musicians (& others too) with open arms.... Fan for life ...not to forget the Chorus & that smile on the face of guy playing keyboards (is that Kaavish?)... All the love. Take a bow. 😊
